title: Birds of Prey (1973) x264 AC3
description:
Harry Walker, ex-military pilot, works for a radio station in Salt Lake City as a traffic helicopter pilot. While on his rounds he observes a bank robbery taking place and the abduction of a female teller. He gives chase, first in their car, then by helicopter.

Some of the best helicopter stunts ever filmed - all pre-CGI.

Note that all releases of this made-for-TV film have had the original soundtrack altered, replaced by P.D. tunes. 

Several scenes show David Janssen singing along to what should be "Three Little Fishies".

This is, however, the best available print.
